name: DAP access levels
definition: Can the institution access individual level data or only aggregate level data (where individual level data refer to individual records and aggregate level data refer to summary tables)?

name: DAP access level completeness
definition: Can the institution access the whole data source or only an extract of the data source?

name: DAP access permissions
definition: Is permission required for your institute to access data source (e.g., from a data controller)?

name: DAP reasons for access
definition: What is the reason for being able to access (an extract of) the data source?

name: Fees
definition: Are there fees for data access?

name: Population subset
definition: If the institution can only access a subset, which subsets can it access?
